@page "/"

<PageTitle>Home</PageTitle>

<header class="bg-dark">
        <BlazorApp1.Client.Layout.NavBar></BlazorApp1.Client.Layout.NavBar>
</header>

<main style="user-select: none;">
    <div class="container py-5">

        <!-- Section 1: PracticeRandomPhrases -->
        <div class="mb-5 text-center">
            <h1 class="display-4">Practice Random Phrases</h1>
            <p class="lead">
                This section allows you to practice random phrases to improve your English comprehension and writing skills.
                Watch the video below to get started.
                Don’t forget to choose the difficulty and then click Next.
                When you see these colors:
            </p>
            <p style="color: green"><span>Correct Question</span></p>
            <p style="color: orange"><span>Probably the question is correct but something is missing!</span></p>
            <p style="color: red"><span>Wrong Question</span></p>
            <div class="ratio ratio-16x9 mt-3" style="user-select: all;">
                <iframe src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/SD2JYCxpk8Q?si=6ZrCiDM65gGQ_Fa2"
                        title="Practice Random Phrases Video"
                        allowfullscreen>
                </iframe>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Section 2: PracticeWordsPhrases -->
        <div class="mb-5 text-center">
            <h1 class="display-4">Practice Words Phrases</h1>
            <p class="lead">
                Here you can practice vocabulary and phrases together. Strengthen your ability to form sentences and understand context.
                Don't forget put the Difficulty and after click and next
                The first time you click Next, it may take a few seconds to show a question.
                When you see this colors in Question or in Traduction:
            </p>
            <p style="color: green"><span>Correct Question</span></p>
            <p style="color: orange"><span>Probably the question is correct but something is missing!</span></p>
            <p style="color: red"><span>Wrong Question</span></p>
            <div class="ratio ratio-16x9 mt-3" style="user-select: all;">
                <iframe src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/Bwqjy6CMED4?si=Lm6gjHzJgTow8b2K"
                        title="Practice Words Video Instructions"
                        allowfullscreen>
                </iframe>
            </div>
        </div>

    </div>
</main>

